    {
      "id": "bs-cordl",
      "versionRange": "*",
      "additionalData": {
        "private": true,
        "_comment": "IMPORTANT: pin this to the bs-cordl release that targets Beat Saber 1.37.0 specifically (check https://qpackages.com/bs-cordl or the BSMG #quest-mod-dev release notes). A '*' or caret-latest range will pull headers for the newest game version and will NOT match 1.37.0's binary layout -- the mod will crash on load. The CI workflow's first run will tell you the resolved version; replace '*' with that exact version pinned (e.g. '=1.4.2') once confirmed."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "paper2_scotland2",
